Basic commands:
--------------
mgl             : Speak on the guild line
mgl :           : Emote on the guild line
channel mages   : Turn on the guild line
muffle mages    : Turn off the guild line
mages           : See which mages are on
gwho            :         "
who             : See what players are on Nirvana.
                  Read 'help_who' for details.
whisper         : A guild tell
form party      : Form an adventuring party
login           : Change your login location
cast            : The command used to invoke a spell
